data.description: Beautiful Mountain Chalet in Golf Course community. Rest and relax on either of the over sized decks to take advantage of shade and sun. Newly refinished hardwoods in living room, a floor to ceiling river rock gas fireplace, new stainless appliances in the kitchen, new carpet in the bedroom, new laminate flooring in the laundry.  Freshly painted.  Upstairs features the master bedroom with new carpeting, and a sizeable loft area. Full unfinished basement and a circular driveway. This can be the perfect getaway or even a full time residence.
